dataSource.query:
SELECT
    event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until final confirmation (days)",
    "Time until confirmation and technical completion (days)",
    "Time until confirmation and closing (days)",
    "Service orders created with immediate basic start date (%)",
    "Service orders released after basic start date (%)",
    "Service orders technically completed after basic finish date (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Service orders finally confirmed")
        	AS "Time until final confirmation (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Service orders confirmed and technically completed") 
        	AS "Time until confirmation and technical completion (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Service orders confirmed and closed")
        	AS "Time until confirmation and closing (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Service orders created with immediate basic start date") * 100
        	AS "Service orders created with immediate basic start date (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Service orders released after basic start date") * 100
        	AS "Service orders released after basic start date (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Service orders technically completed after basic finish date") * 100
        	AS "Service orders technically completed after basic finish date (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
